{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Compulsory to display country of manufacture on all goods at point of sale",
        "additional_details": "There appears to be a growing interest in the UK population to support UK manufacturing, industry and businesses and it is currently very difficult to determine (particularly when shopping online) the country of manufacture/origin of goods and services. It should be made a compulsory and legal requirement to declare this information at the point of sale. This will provide UK consumers with the opportunity to make a more informed decision of choice.",
        "background": "Change the Law to make it a compulsory and legal requirement to clearly display, at the point of sale, the country of manufacture and origin on all goods and services sold in the uk",
